overview: On January 21st GCW: Take a Picture 2023 is live on FITE+ straight from Von Braun Center in Huntsville, AL. The first matches are already announced, check them below:  Billie Starkz vs Sawyer Wreck  GCW World Tag Team Championship  Los Macizos vs Jordan Oliver & Nick Wayne  Tony Deppen vs Adam Priest  Blake Christian vs Cabana Man Dan  Marko Stunt vs Mike Jackson  ...and much more!
title: GCW Take a Picture
